headline: ACM Research Set to Join S&P SmallCap 600
summary: ACM Research Inc. (NASD: ACMR) will replace WK Kellogg Co. (NYSE: KLG) in the S&P SmallCap 600 effective prior to the opening of trading on Friday, September 26. The Ferrero Group is acquiring WK Kellogg in a deal expected to close soon, pending final closing conditions.

headline: Port Performance Varies Across the Globe Amid Continuing Shocks
summary: Port performance across the world declined between 2020 and 2024 due to the Red Sea Crisis, challenges at the Panama Canal, and pandemic-related shocks, according to a new report released today. However, efficiency gains varied by region and income level.
